      "description": "## Hex Cartographer v1.0.0\r\n\r\nInitial release of Hex Cartographer — a visual hex map editor for Obsidian.\r\n\r\n### Features\r\n- Infinite scrollable hex grid canvas\r\n- 25+ hand-crafted symbols (Extras, Vegetation, Mountains, Buildings)\r\n- Rivers, roads & borders with customizable styles\r\n- Text annotations with vault links\r\n- Color palettes and pattern stamp tool\r\n- Export as PNG/JPEG, print support\r\n- Full mobile support with touch gestures\r\n- 11 languages supported\r\n",
